WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:20.790 align:middle line:90%


00:00:20.790 --> 00:00:24.255 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:24.255 --> 00:00:50.530 align:middle line:90%


00:00:50.530 --> 00:00:55.150 align:middle line:84%
>> In 2006, I attempted suicide
whilst I was on a high dosage

00:00:55.150 --> 00:00:59.500 align:middle line:84%
of medication for what my doctor
diagnosed as major depressive

00:00:59.500 --> 00:01:01.030 align:middle line:90%
disorder.

00:01:01.030 --> 00:01:02.620 align:middle line:90%
It was my second attempt.

00:01:02.620 --> 00:01:05.950 align:middle line:84%
The first time, I
was only a teenager.

00:01:05.950 --> 00:01:08.410 align:middle line:84%
After having depression
since childhood,

00:01:08.410 --> 00:01:11.920 align:middle line:84%
I was told I would most likely
need to remain on medication

00:01:11.920 --> 00:01:14.050 align:middle line:90%
for the rest of my life.

00:01:14.050 --> 00:01:16.780 align:middle line:84%
This prospect only further
added to my depression

00:01:16.780 --> 00:01:20.980 align:middle line:84%
because deep down, I knew
I was only just existing.

00:01:20.980 --> 00:01:24.930 align:middle line:84%
I was numb inside, and sleep was
my constant escape in a world

00:01:24.930 --> 00:01:28.710 align:middle line:84%
that I was unable
to fully experience.

00:01:28.710 --> 00:01:30.780 align:middle line:90%
It hasn't been an easy journey.

00:01:30.780 --> 00:01:35.590 align:middle line:84%
In fact, it has been the
greatest challenge of my life.

00:01:35.590 --> 00:01:39.860 align:middle line:84%
But I can humbly say that
I transformed my death wish

00:01:39.860 --> 00:01:43.070 align:middle line:90%
into a huge life wish.

00:01:43.070 --> 00:01:47.240 align:middle line:84%
I finally found health
and happiness within.

00:01:47.240 --> 00:01:53.760 align:middle line:84%
My so-called chemical imbalance
in the brain no longer exists.

00:01:53.760 --> 00:01:56.150 align:middle line:84%
I lost 20 kilos
and no longer have

00:01:56.150 --> 00:02:01.610 align:middle line:84%
symptoms of depression, anxiety,
panic attacks, chronic fatigue,

00:02:01.610 --> 00:02:04.280 align:middle line:90%
high cholesterol, and anemia.

00:02:04.280 --> 00:02:06.770 align:middle line:84%
I am completely
medication-free because I

00:02:06.770 --> 00:02:10.020 align:middle line:90%
chose to do whatever it takes.

00:02:10.020 --> 00:02:11.910 align:middle line:90%
I changed my beliefs.

00:02:11.910 --> 00:02:13.890 align:middle line:90%
I changed my diet.

00:02:13.890 --> 00:02:16.470 align:middle line:90%
I began yoga and meditating.

00:02:16.470 --> 00:02:18.420 align:middle line:90%
I changed my life.

00:02:18.420 --> 00:02:22.350 align:middle line:84%
And with the support of a loving
husband and children and those

00:02:22.350 --> 00:02:27.210 align:middle line:84%
that loved me, I followed my own
heart and what I innately knew,

00:02:27.210 --> 00:02:31.830 align:middle line:84%
which was guiding me inwards
towards my interconnected

00:02:31.830 --> 00:02:33.960 align:middle line:90%
relationship with nature itself.

00:02:33.960 --> 00:02:36.960 align:middle line:90%


00:02:36.960 --> 00:02:39.300 align:middle line:90%
No one could do it for me.

00:02:39.300 --> 00:02:44.250 align:middle line:84%
I knew that the only true
form of help is self-help.

00:02:44.250 --> 00:02:47.820 align:middle line:84%
Today, I live as though
each day is precious,

00:02:47.820 --> 00:02:50.700 align:middle line:84%
with self-love and gratitude
for this experience

00:02:50.700 --> 00:02:53.100 align:middle line:90%
and all that unfolds.

00:02:53.100 --> 00:02:57.390 align:middle line:84%
The innate gratitude, peace,
health, and happiness I feel

00:02:57.390 --> 00:03:01.800 align:middle line:84%
humbles me to the core,
and my outer world now

00:03:01.800 --> 00:03:04.560 align:middle line:90%
mirrors my new inner world.

00:03:04.560 --> 00:03:07.440 align:middle line:84%
Health was my motivation,
and the weight also

00:03:07.440 --> 00:03:11.130 align:middle line:84%
naturally took care of
itself as my body detoxified

00:03:11.130 --> 00:03:13.440 align:middle line:90%
and came back into balance.

00:03:13.440 --> 00:03:16.560 align:middle line:84%
No pills, no shake,
no diet food,

00:03:16.560 --> 00:03:18.960 align:middle line:84%
no counting points
and calories--

00:03:18.960 --> 00:03:24.120 align:middle line:84%
just an abundance of
nature's living plant foods.

00:03:24.120 --> 00:03:26.310 align:middle line:84%
I no longer have any
cravings for food

00:03:26.310 --> 00:03:29.410 align:middle line:84%
that doesn't add
more life to my body.

00:03:29.410 --> 00:03:33.740 align:middle line:84%
I still have delicious desserts,
treats, and even cheese,

00:03:33.740 --> 00:03:36.790 align:middle line:84%
but they're all made
of fruits and nuts.

00:03:36.790 --> 00:03:39.660 align:middle line:84%
I've developed a new
loving relationship

00:03:39.660 --> 00:03:43.170 align:middle line:84%
with food that's nourishing
to me both physically

00:03:43.170 --> 00:03:45.000 align:middle line:90%
and spiritually.

00:03:45.000 --> 00:03:47.670 align:middle line:84%
I no longer choose to put
food into my body that

00:03:47.670 --> 00:03:51.090 align:middle line:84%
comes from the energy of
cruelty, suffering, violence,

00:03:51.090 --> 00:03:52.230 align:middle line:90%
and death.

00:03:52.230 --> 00:03:54.450 align:middle line:84%
The food I choose
to put into my body

00:03:54.450 --> 00:03:56.820 align:middle line:84%
contains the Earth's
vital life force

00:03:56.820 --> 00:04:01.080 align:middle line:84%
and nourishment, which then
transfers into my cells,

00:04:01.080 --> 00:04:03.139 align:middle line:90%
giving me more life.

