doctor to fix us.

01:12:19.700 --> 01:12:23.690 align:middle line:84%
We can tend to find
ourselves looking for excuses

01:12:23.690 --> 01:12:26.550 align:middle line:84%
so that we don't need
to take responsibility.

01:12:26.550 --> 01:12:28.640 align:middle line:84%
Another thing we
need to realize is

01:12:28.640 --> 01:12:32.590 align:middle line:84%
that we can't expect our
doctors to know everything.

01:12:32.590 --> 01:12:37.580 align:middle line:84%
A GP, after all, is a
general practitioner.

01:12:37.580 --> 01:12:39.410 align:middle line:90%
We go to the doctor.

01:12:39.410 --> 01:12:44.450 align:middle line:84%
He or she diagnoses
what they think

01:12:44.450 --> 01:12:49.010 align:middle line:84%
we have according to the
symptoms we are presenting with

01:12:49.010 --> 01:12:52.730 align:middle line:84%
