for what is generally

01:12:52.730 --> 01:12:56.170 align:middle line:90%
used to treat that condition.

01:12:56.170 --> 01:12:59.640 align:middle line:84%
So what we find
happening is that we

01:12:59.640 --> 01:13:03.420 align:middle line:84%
are given a prescription
for medication

01:13:03.420 --> 01:13:07.110 align:middle line:84%
to take away the swelling,
medication to take away

01:13:07.110 --> 01:13:08.820 align:middle line:90%
the pain.

01:13:08.820 --> 01:13:13.650 align:middle line:84%
What we're doing is we're
treating the symptoms and not

01:13:13.650 --> 01:13:15.610 align:middle line:90%
the cause.

01:13:15.610 --> 01:13:19.860 align:middle line:84%
So if we were driving
our car down the road,

01:13:19.860 --> 01:13:23.240 align:middle line:84%
and a red flashing light
came on the dashboard,

01:13:23.240 --> 01:13:29.070 align:middle line:84%
do we pull over and find the
cause of the warning light?

01:13:29.070 --> 01:13:33.420 align:middle line:84%
Or do we continue to
drive and just disconnect

01:13:33.420 --> 01:13:37.630 align:middle line:84%
the red flashing light so
that the symptoms are gone,

01:13:37.630 --> 01:13:41.860 align:middle line:84%
but the underlying
cause is still there?

01:13:41.860 --> 01:13:45.000 align:middle line:84%
And if we do nothing
but treat the symptoms,

01:13:45.000 --> 01:13:47.620 align:middle line:90%
the cause is still there.

01:13:47.620 --> 01:13:49.980 align:middle line:90%
We're heading for a disaster.

01:13:49.980 --> 01:13:53.970 align:middle line:84%
We must also acknowledge that
we have a medical system which

01:13:53.970 --> 01:13:59.340 align:middle line:84%
