that's fantastic for trauma,

01:14:04.620 --> 01:14:08.170 align:middle line:84%
for tissue injuries,
for broken bones,

01:14:08.170 --> 01:14:10.360 align:middle line:84%
for putting bodies
back together.

01:14:10.360 --> 01:14:15.450 align:middle line:84%
But for disease management,
the system is sadly lacking.

01:14:15.450 --> 01:14:20.750 align:middle line:84%
A pill for every ill is a system
built on treating symptoms

01:14:20.750 --> 01:14:22.700 align:middle line:90%
